CLASS       Hydrolases;
            Acting on ester bonds;
            Phosphoric-monoester hydrolases
SYSNAME     beta-L-galactose-1-phosphate phosphohydrolase
REACTION    beta-L-galactose 1-phosphate + H2O = L-galactose + phosphate [RN:R07674]
